title: The Queen's Gambit - Sygrayem (Piano Cover)
description:
Hey there, this is my 4th cover from this soundtrack. I don't know which other ones to cover so if you have suggestions; please and thank you.
I am now looking into starting tutorial videos soon. I'm getting some softwares and once I get a look that I like and good work flow, I'll start uploading my older arrangement as tutorials until they are all done and you can learn them!
I'm also looking into having them on the music platforms. I'll let you know when you can stream my covers!
Thanks a lot for watching.
I do all my arrangement by ear so no sheets...maybe soon tho :)
